<p><b>Computer security</b> is <a href="Information_security" title="Information security">information security</a> as applied to <a href="Computer" title="Computer">computers</a> and networks.</p>
<p>The field covers all the processes and mechanisms by which computer-based equipment, information and services are protected from unintended or unauthorized access, change or destruction. Computer security also includes protection from unplanned events and natural disasters.</p>
